	<h1>Your Favorite Movies Reviews</h1>
	<p> Paperclip is maintained and funded by thoughtbot. The names and logos for thoughtbot are trademarks of thoughtbot, inc.

We love open source software! See our other projects or hire us to design, develop, and grow your product.</p>
<p> <%= link_to "Sign Up To Write A Review", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %> </p>

</div>
